showInside.title: Show
showInside.description:
Determines whether this entity will be shown inside or outside of a mask with the given ID.
If multiple ID's are passed: 
- If 'Inside' is chosen, only the parts which are inside all of the given IDs will be shown.
- If 'Outside' is chosen, the parts which are outside any of the given IDs will be shown.

maskID.title: Mask ID
maskID.description: This mask id should be an integer between 0 and 7, as it relates as the power of 2 to the actual mask id.
